      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOHO CRUNCH TIME (6) is a colt by Captain Crunch on debut for a strong juvenile yard in Michael Stanley. Has shown ability in finishing runner-up in two trials at Menangle. Big chance to kick off with a win. REVVIN REYNARD (10) made it three placings in as many runs this time in when he came from this row and worked but stuck on for a 2m second at this circuit and distance last week. Chased the smart Don Hunter at Menangle in his other two outings since a spell. Close to a win. TINY PRANCER (3) is stepping out for the first time. By Bling It On and hails from the Kerryann Morris stable. Runner-up to Group 1 winner Birdsong in his latest trial in the city and should have no excuses from this advantageous draw. UNJUST ENRICHMENT (9) missed narrowly fresh before breaking the maiden with a last-start win by 3 metres at this circuit and distance. Draws for a trail and has upside.",
